# ui/ (Vue frontend) - node_modules and its own cache are never committed.
# Its build output IS committed at internal/webui/dist (see that
# package's doc comment): a bare `go build` must work on a fresh clone
# without Node installed, so CI/goreleaser always rebuild it fresh before
# compiling, but a checked-in baseline keeps go-only contributors unblocked.
ui/node_modules/
ui/.vite/
ui/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
